    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎加入公司，船员……准备好清除异常了吗?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <strong>Anomaly Company</strong> 中，你和你的船员被派去评估现实。在这款支持最多 4 人联机合作的恐怖游戏中，你们将进入逼真而诡异的“阈限空间”环境，仔细记住周围的一切，并找出令人不安的异常现象。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你必须判断时间线是否安全。一次错误的决定——一切将被重置。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你，准备好收容这些异常时间线了吗?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099190/extras/0a323e6d16b2e0efcd3db6048d5d8bdb.poster.avif?t=1772324393\" width=1170 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099190/extras/0a323e6d16b2e0efcd3db6048d5d8bdb.webm?t=1772324393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099190/extras/0a323e6d16b2e0efcd3db6048d5d8bdb.mp4?t=1772324393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法介绍</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1–4 人在线合作</strong>  <br>你可以单人游玩，或与最多 4 名玩家在线合作，体验紧张刺激的合作恐怖玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过语音聊天或文字聊天进行沟通，分析环境、分享发现，并争论是否存在异常。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>作为船员的职责</strong>    <br>每一关都从稳定状态开始。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >记住环境细节，随后密切观察可能出现的细微变化、诡异异常以及恐怖事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >判断时间线是否安全，或是否必须清除，才能继续前进。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独立开发者项目</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Anomaly Company</strong> 是我独立一人开发的项目。<br>所有功能、更新和修复都由我亲自完成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因此，开发进度可能会比大型工作室慢一些——<br>但这也意味着游戏是用心制作的，充满热情，并且非常重视玩家的反馈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099190/extras/2887b888dd09284118391f6281e7a0ad.avif?t=1772324393\" width=1560 height=176 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你可以在 Anomaly Company 中体验的内容</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1–4 人在线合作</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合作恐怖玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高重复可玩性</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >语音聊天与文字聊天</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逼真且充满阈限感的环境</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >令人不安的异常现象与跳跃惊吓</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以观察为核心的玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多张独特地图，每张都有不同的场景与大量异常</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >进入一个令人极度不安、仿佛真实存在的世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099190/extras/527b31990f77b529b71fd17384de869f.poster.avif?t=1772324393\" width=1170 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099190/extras/527b31990f77b529b71fd17384de869f.webm?t=1772324393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099190/extras/527b31990f77b529b71fd17384de869f.mp4?t=1772324393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >直面荒诞的异常、混乱与不可预测的恐怖</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099190/extras/52b6d463830f7261a66a22636f93a72b.poster.avif?t=1772324393\" width=1170 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099190/extras/52b6d463830f7261a66a22636f93a72b.webm?t=1772324393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099190/extras/52b6d463830f7261a66a22636f93a72b.mp4?t=1772324393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >遵循协议。 信任你的船员。 让公司感到骄傲。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099190/extras/fab665d2dd6f44b6861b1f3267a31e27.poster.avif?t=1772324393\" width=1170 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099190/extras/fab665d2dd6f44b6861b1f3267a31e27.webm?t=1772324393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099190/extras/fab665d2dd6f44b6861b1f3267a31e27.mp4?t=1772324393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你为 Anomaly Company 工作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >相信你的记忆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >质疑现实。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >---</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>界面与字幕仅支持英文</i></p>",
